@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qwnwec(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.11 + tmp + 0.39)) * wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = 1.00
    tmp = (wp.exp(v1) + wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.14)))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = (v1 - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.77) + 0.79))
    data[tid] = v0
